[/quote]

if they were around the wrong way, does that mean a bot would work in opposite direction ? ^_^[/quote]
Nope, it would fail calculating screen positions and such, because the x and y positions are switched around.
(So most likely it says you’re on a tile, which isn’t located on the screen, unless you’re at the center ofcourse)
